ref="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%AD/K%C3%BD-nh%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-8Hqk1VYkMZ9FlHN3Nhts8Q">Ký nhân kỳ 1 - 寄人其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%AD/author-7wu4PrmaDd9EvB6ALgax_g">Trương Bí</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%E1%BB%8B-h%E1%BB%AFu-ki%E1%BB%81u-bi%C3%AAn-ph%E1%BA%A5t-di%E1%BB%87n-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-Mq2fsrtgKI-wHZDD7ctHgA">Liễu (Vị hữu kiều biên phất diện hương) - 柳（為有橋邊拂面香）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/T%C3%A1i-du-Huy%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%C3%B4-qu%C3%A1n/poem-CPaTw3AaiaruMfTnljeRsQ">Tái du Huyền Đô quán - 再遊玄都觀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/author-EjtGFCLaQR-cL2GZdcpbaQ">Lưu Vũ Tích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/Tr%C3%B9ng-%C4%91%C4%83ng-Ng%E1%BB%B1-Long-t%E1%BB%B1-chung-c%C3%A1c-Canh-Tu%E1%BA%A5t/poem-lZPyG_0ciQWIStZ3eohOnQ">Trùng đăng Ngự Long tự chung các (Canh Tuất) - 重登御龍寺鍾閣（庚戌）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/author-qsdCXtvu8PM8SdkWmraV5A">Phạm Đình Hổ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
